{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-challenges-classic-show-tsx","path":"/learn/project-euler/project-euler-problems-201-to-300/problem-214-totient-chains","result":{"data":{"challengeNode":{"challenge":{"block":"project-euler-problems-201-to-300","demoType":null,"title":"Vežba 214: Lanac totijenta","description":"<section id=\"description\">\n<p>Neka je $\\phi$ funkcija totijenta Eulera, tj. za prirodan broj $n$, $\\phi(n)$ je broj $k$, $1 ≤ k ≤ n$, za koje je $gcd(k,n) = 1$.</p>\n<p>Ponavljanjem korišćenja $φ$, svaki pozitivan broj formira opadajuću sekvencu brojeva koja se završava sa 1. Na primer, počevši od 5, formira se niz 5,4,2,1. Evo spiska svih nizova dužine 4:</p>\n<p>$$\\begin{align}\n5,4,2,1 &#x26; \\\\\n7,6,2,1 &#x26; \\\\\n8,4,2,1 &#x26; \\\\\n9,6,2,1 &#x26; \\\\\n10,4,2,1 &#x26; \\\\\n12,4,2,1 &#x26; \\\\\n14,6,2,1 &#x26; \\\\\n18,6,2,1 &#x26;\n\\end{align}$$</p>\n<p>Postoje samo dve lance među ovim koje počinju sa osnovnim brojem, a njihov ukupan zbir je 12.</p>\n<p>Koja je suma svih baznih brojeva ispod $40\\,000\\,000$ koji generišu niz dužine 25?</p>\n</section>","id":"5900f4421000cf542c50ff55","hasEditableBoundaries":false,"instructions":"","notes":null,"challengeType":1,"helpCategory":"Euler","videoUrl":null,"superBlock":"project-euler","translationPending":false,"forumTopicId":301856,"hooks":null,"fields":{"slug":"/learn/project-euler/project-euler-problems-201-to-300/problem-214-totient-chains"},"required":[],"usesMultifileEditor":false,"challengeFiles":[{"fileKey":"scriptjs","ext":"js","name":"script","contents":"function totientChains() {\n\n  return true;\n}\n\ntotientChains();","head":null,"tail":null,"editableRegionBoundaries":[],"history":["script.js"]}],"saveSubmissionToDB":null,"tests":[{"text":"<p><code>totientChains()</code> treba da vrati <code>1677366278943</code>.</p>","testString":"assert.strictEqual(totientChains(), 1677366278943);"}]}}},"pageContext":{"challengeMeta":{"blockHashSlug":"/learn/project-euler/#project